latestIgtvVideos.title: SPRUCE men's skin care 🤎
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Not a big coffee lover, I've now started liking coffee in my skin care ever since I tried this @spruceshaveclub ORGANIC COFFEE FACE WASH which perfectly fits my skin and is best for tan removal. It not only cleanses the skin thoroughly but also protects and nourishes it.
.
. 
The best thing about this face wash is that it's an organic product with all natural ingredients in it and no parabens, sulphates or mineral oils.
It has glycolic acid which helps wash away the dead skin cells leaving the skin even toned and all brightened up.
The citric acid in it helps with mild breakouts, pigmentation, dark spots and enlarged pores while the glycerine and aloe vera extracts help retain the moisture along with the soothing effects of menthol.
.
.
For even better experience, combine it with @spruceshaveclub DE-TAN PEEL-OFF FACE MASK, which is a blend of coffee, glycolic acid and multani mitti and works as a good exfoliator removing all the dirt and impurities from the skin adding to the brightness and glow.
.
.
Specially curated for men, the  spruce de-tan range is a must try for every guy.
.
.
If you also wish to fight your daily skin issues, go give this one a try. It's easily available @amazondotin
.
.
.
.
.
